{"tid":2129432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"習雲長水淹7軍","createTime":"2020-07-28T14:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T14:49:31.000Z","uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"50a310a189863dba277ae0c9abade3cd6d774048","tid":2129432,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"長江上游今年以來最大洪水，今日過境重慶主城，寸灘水文站首次出現超警戒水位，嘉陵江邊的磁器口古鎮水位達到184.07米，超出警戒水位3米多，數十商舖被浸。江水亦淹沒重慶地標建築朝天門的平台，水位達到朝天門門洞中部。<br />\n重慶水城<br />\n支那人既中國式水都<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"purple\">下一句 習雲長兵敗走北京</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n水位繼續上全力上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}